    API -.-> OAuth
    API -.-> HTTPS
    API -.-> Rate
    
    %% Environment Connections
    Dev --> Local
    Dev --> Mock
    Prod --> Gunicorn
    Prod --> CloudDB

    %% Legend
    subgraph Legend["Legend"]
        direction LR
        L1[("Frontend")]:::frontend
        L2[("Backend")]:::backend
        L3[("Cloud")]:::cloud
        L4[("Database")]:::database
        L5[("Security")]:::security
    end

